\begin_layout Section*
Restrictions
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This work will deal with the combination of a high level multi-agent and
 a robot platform.
 Current technologies in Multi-Agent-Systems (MAS) and Mobile Robotics will
 be used to achieve high level task flexibility.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Also there might be implemented specilized algorithms, e.g.
 for robot control, mostly out-of-the box drivers and interfaces will be
 used.
 Especially the Multi-Agent-System shall be used and is assumed to provide
 already:
\end_layout

